      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "COOTAMUNDRA LAD (2) lines up chasing another win after scoring over 275m at this track in 16.13, set up by a fast early sectional. Well placed and will be tough to beat. CHEDDAR MONELLI (1) hit the ground running and set it up early clocking 16.06 with a half a length win at this track over 275m. Has a strong record out of this box with three wins and four minor placings from seven starts. In sparkling form and looks the one to beat again. QUEST FOR STEPS (8) jumped well and stalked the lead before boxing on to finish second (17.21) at Mandurah in Grade 5. Failed to fire only run here. Hard to beat again. TRUNKEY FRANK (7) jumps at a shorter journey and still warrants respect.",
